\id TIT - Gamo Full Bible final version 
\h Titoosas 
\toc1 Phawuloosi Titoosas Xaafida Kiita 
\toc2 Titoosas 
\toc3 Tito 
\mt2 Phawuloosi 
\mt1 Titoosas 
\mt2 Xaafida Kiita 
\imt1 Giddo Qofa 
\ip Titoosi Ayzaabeteththafe simmi ammanon gelidi Phawuloosa, Mishiraachcho qaalaa ooson matan maaddiza izas adda erettida lagge. Phawuloosi hayssa ha kiitaza xaafiday baappe layththan yoogizanne izara matiza banara issife ooththiza Titoosas gidishin Titoosi he wode Woosa Keeththa xeellishe Qarxeese geetettizason dees; ha kiitay lo7eththi minththizay heedzdzu ayfe yo7ota bolla. 
\ip Koyroy Woosa keeththa cimati harappeka Qarxeese asaas iita ooso gishshas isttas ay mala lo7o oosoy bessizaakko Titoosi istta tamaarsana mala Titoosa qofsees. Nam7anththozi Woosa Keeththa giddon diza dumma dumma butten hessika cimmida maccassatanne attuma asaa; hessaththoka naateththa naytanne asas ooththi aqizayta izi tamaarsana bessizayssa tamaarsana mala Titoosa zorees. Wurseththan qasse ammanon duussa gishshas harappeka asay saroninne siiqoteththan de7ana malassa; hessaththoka Woosa Keeththa giddofe issoy issaa ixo, ooshshinne ba garsan shaaketeth aggana mala Titoosas zore immidi ooththana oge bessides. 
\iot Ha Maxaafay Oykkida Kumeththa Qofa 
\io1 Geloso \ior 1:1-4\ior* 
\io1 Woosa keeththa kaaleththizayta \ior 1:5-16\ior* 
\io1 Woosa keeththan diza dumma dumma asatas imettida ooso \ior 2:1-15\ior* 
\io1 Zorenne naagettana mala qofso \ior 3:1-11\ior* 
\io1 Kuushsha qofa \ior 3:12-15\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Woosa Keeth Kaaleththizaytanne Wordo Astamaareta 
\p  
\v 1 Xoossas doorettidayta ammanoninne Tumu Ayanan kaaleththiza tumaa erateththan dichchana mala Xoossa ayllenne Yesus Kirstoosa Hawaare gidida Phawuloosappe,  
\v 2 iza ammanoynne erateththay kaseppe oykkidi wordotontta Goday daro wodeppe kase ba immida mernaa de7o hidota mala.  
\v 3 Izi kase gida wodey gakkida mala nuna ashshida Xoossaa azazon taas sabbakanaas imettida hara baggara Xoossi ba qaalaa qonccisides. 
\p  
\v 4 Nuus koththe gidida ammano issifeteththaan, ammanon taas tumu naa gidida Titoosas, «Xoossaa Aawappenne nuna ashshida Yesus Kirstoosappe kiyateththinne saroteththi nees gido» gides.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2Qoro 8:23; Gala 2:3; 2Xim 4:10\x* 
\s1 Qarxeesen Titoosa Ooso 
\p  
\v 5 Ta nena Qarxeesen aggiday buroppe giigana bessiza daro miishshi diza gishshas ne giigsanaassinne ta nena azazida mala katamay dizason Woosa Keeththa cimata ne dooranaassa.  
\v 6 Cimateththan doorettanayti istta bolla wosoy bayndayta, issi machchi azinata, nayti ammanizaytanne waayisonttayta woykko azazettiza nayta aawata gidetto.  
\v 7 Woosa keeththa cimay Xoossas ooththana hadara ekkidaade gidida mala iza bolla wosoy bayndaade gidanaas bessees; hessika ceeqettizaade, guuththa miishshan yiillotizaadenne maththottizaade, ushshanchchanne izas bessontta ogera go7a gididaaz gooddi ekki bizaade gidanaas bessenna.  
\v 8 Hessafe bollara izi imath mokkizaade, lo7o ooso dosizaade, barkka bana haarizaade, suure as, xillonne baas naagettizaade gidanaas bessees.  
\v 9 Hara asata lo7o timirten minththeththizaadenne he lo7o timirteza ixxizayta hanqanaas ba tamaarda mala qaalaan minnizaade gidanaas bessees. 
\p  
\v 10 Waayisizaytinne doonan xalla baleththizayti daroti deettes; harappeka heyti qaxxarettida Ayhuda asatappe ammanida asata baggata.  
\v 11 Heytantta co7u histteth bessees; gaasoykka istti bessontta ogera baas go7a demmanaas bessontta timirte tamaarson keeththa asaa wursi mooron deettes.  
\v 12 Istta nabetappe issaadey istta gishshas haasayshe, «Qarxeese asay ubba wode wordanchchata, iita do7ata, ganjamatanne azallata» gides.  
\v 13 He markkateththay tuma; hessa gishshas ne istta lo7eththa hanqetta; gaasoykka isttas tumu ammanoy daana malanne,  
\v 14 Ayhudata haysi7e woykko tumu yo7oppe haakkida asata azazo istti siyontta malassa.  
\v 15 Geeshshatas miishshi wurikka geeshsha shin tunatassinne ammanonttaytas gidikko wurikka tuna; harappeka istta qofay wurikka tunides.  
\v 16 Istti bana nuni Xoos eroos geettes shin ba hanoteththaan gidikko kaddeettes; istti harassizayta, azazettonttaytanne lo7o oosos bessonttayta. 
\c 2  
\s1 Tumu Timirte 
\p  
\v 1 Neni gidikko asaa tumu gididaaz tamaarsa.  
\v 2 Cima asay wozinama, bonchchettidayta, bana barkka haarizayta, ammanoninne siiqon, dandayankka lo7o gidana mala ne istta zora.  
\v 3 Hessaththoka cima maccassati ba diza duussan bonchchora dizaytanne lo7o hanoteth asa tamaarsizayta gidetto attiin asa sunth iissizayta woykko woyne cajje ushsha suuken waaxettidayta gidontta mala istta tamaarsa.  
\v 4 Hessaththo ooththiko naateththa maccassati ba azinatanne ba nayta dosana mala tamaarsanaas dandayeettes.  
\v 5 Xoossa qaalay oona achchanka cayettontta mala istti barkka bana haarizaytanne geeshshata, keeththa giddon istta oosoy oykkidaytanne asas kiyata, ba azinatas azazettizayta gidana mala cima maccassati istta tamaarsetto. 
\p  
\v 6 Hessaththoka yelaga attumasay barkka bana haarana mala ne istta zora.  
\v 7 Ay hanonkka ne asas lo7o leemiso gida; neni asaa tamaarsiza timirteza nenikka wozinappe tamaarsizaadenne naagizaade gida.  
\v 8 Nu gishshas iita haasayza asay haasayanaas iita demmontta aggidi yeellatana mala ne haasayza haasaya giddon borso yo7oy dooppo.  
\v 9 Aylleti aazankka ba godatas haarettana malanne ufayssana mala; qasseka awute zaarontta mala tamaarsa.  
\v 10 Hanizaazan ubbaan nuna ashshida Xoossa timirtey dosettana mala istti lo7o markkateth bessana mala ba godata miish kaysotoppetto. 
\p  
\v 11 Asas izappe maaroy beettiza Xoossa kiyateththi asa ubbaas qonccides.  
\v 12 He kiyateththika nuni nagaran duussinne ha alame amoteththaa kaddidi hayssa ha wodezan nurkka nuna haaridinne xilloteththan Tumu Ayana duus daanayssa nuna tamaarssees.  
\v 13 Hessika nuus anjjettida hidota gidida wogga Xoossaanne nuna ashshida Yesus Kirstoosa bonchchoy qonccanayssa naaganaassa.  
\v 14 Izikka nuna iitateththaafe wozzanaassinne lo7o ooththanaas minniza ba dere baas dooranaas bana nuus aaththi immides.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt Maza 130:8; Kessa 19:5; Zaare 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 1Phex 2:9\x* 
\p  
\v 15 Hessa gishshas ne tamaarsanayti heytantta; hessaka ne kumeththa godateththara zoranne hanqa; nena oonikka leqqofo. 
\c 3  
\s1 Lo7o Ooso 
\p  
\v 1 Asay dere ayssizaytas haarettana malanne lo7o gidida miish wursi ooththanaas giiga gidana mala asaa qofsa.  
\v 2 Qasseka oonikka asa bolla iita haasayontta malanne lo7o asa gidana mala asa ubbaas kumeththa wozinappe ba ashketeth bessana mala ubbaa qofsa.  
\v 3 Nunikka kase qofay bayndayta, azazettonttayta, balettizayta, dumma dumma amoninne lo7o duussas aylleteththan haarettizayta; asaranne nurkka nu garsankka ooyettishe iitateththaninne miqqayneteththan doos.  
\v 4-5 Gido attiin nuna ashshida Xoossaa kiyateththinne iza siiqoy qonccida wode nu ooththida Xilloteththaan gidontta dishin iza maaroteththa daron attidos; izi nuna ashshiday nam7anththo yeleteth gidida meechchaninne Xillo Ayanan ooraxeteththanna.  
\v 6 Hessaka Xillo Ayanay nu bolla nu Godaa Xoossi nuna ashshida Yesus Kirstoosa baggara darssi gussides.  
\v 7 Hessika nu iza kiyateththan xillidi mernaa de7o hidota oykkidi laattizayta gidanaassa.  
\v 8 Hessika ammanettida qaala; Xoossaa ammanizayti lo7o oosos bana aaththi immana mala hayssa wursa ne lo7eththa yootana mala ta koyays; hessika lo7onne ay asikka koyzaaza.  
\v 9 Qasseka hada palamappenne asay ba qommo qoodizaazappe, marshefenne woga gishshas dendiza ooshshafe ne haakka; heytantti go7ay baynda paththontta yo7o.  
\v 10 Asa giddon shaaketeth medhdhiza asi issito nam7uto ne zoriin ekkontta ixxiko izaadera nees issifeteththi dooppo.  
\v 11 Hessa mala asi balettida nagaranchcha asa; izaadey barkka ba bolla pirdidayssa ne era. 
\s1 Wurseththa Zore 
\p  
\v 12 Arximoone woykko Tiqiqoosa ta neekko kiittiko ne taakko Niqopholiyoone yaanaas nees dandayettizaaz wursa ooththa; tani ha layththa balgo heen aaththana gaada qachchadis.\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Hawa 20:4; Efe 6:21-22; Qola 4:7-8; 2Xim 4:12\x* 
\v 13 Woga eriza Zeemaasinne Aphiloosi bishin isttas koshshizaaz wursa kunththa maadda.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt Hawa 18:24; 1Qoro 16:12\x* 
\v 14 Nu baggatas hachchis hachchis istta koshshizaaz istti demmana malanne istta deeththay go7ay bayndaaz gidontta mala istti lo7o ooso ooththi minnana mala tamaaranaas koshshees. 
\p  
\v 15 Tanara dizayti inttena saro geettes; ammano gaason nuna siiqizayta ubbaa saro giite; Xoossa kiyateththi inttenara gido.